thread.title: Darryl Mogg
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Darryl Mogg

author: Darryl Mogg
title: Darryl Mogg
text: Very good company cheap rates and no hassle collect or return...One thing I would say ...We took out full cover insurance which covered us for everything...However we were told we could only claim once and if we had another crash/bump then we would have to pay excess $2000 didn't think this was fair as we had paid premium for the full 14 days....Would recommend this company
